<figureCitation box="[179,260,1941,1960]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="3.[129,168,1387,1406]" captionTargetBox="[129,1452,174,1370]" captionTargetId="figure-352@3.[129,1452,174,1370]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Fig. 2. Hoplias malabaricus karyotypes (karyomorph A) with fluorescent in situ hybridization (FISH) using 5S rDNA (a, d, g), 18S rDNA (b, e, h) and 5SHindIII satellite DNA (c, f, i) probes in the populations from the basins of the São Francisco (a, b, c), Araguaia (d, e, f) and Xingu (g, h, i) Rivers. Scale bar = 5μm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5421619" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5421619/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">Fig. 2h</figureCitation>
